txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Ruffled feathers from the birds to the north and west of Esteldín. Deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
'We will get to work on these, thank you.'
'The ruffled feathers can further be used to fit bedding. Can you help us?'
Rangers of Esteldín Task: Ruffled Feathers
Ferrif, a Ranger, has asked for a collection of ruffled feathers to be delivered to him at the Ranger's home at Esteldín.
Deliver the ruffled feathers to Ferrif in Esteldín
You have accepted a task to collect ruffled feathers from the birds in the area surrounding Esteldín to the north and west. Once collected, you are to deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
Wanted: Ruffled feathers from the birds to the north and west of Esteldín.
